{"tid":268982,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"清水富美加出家「幸福的科學」4個月爆婚訊 對象是教主的兒子","createTime":"2017-06-03T12:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T14:15:32.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"530f090a5f62126efff1ee8fc23f09d4fccc4b3e","tid":268982,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"日本女星清水富美加年初2月閃電宣布引退出家，投入新興宗教「幸福的科學」，丟給娛樂圈一記超大震撼彈。她和前東家解約，改取法名「千眼美子」，還剪去招牌長髮，隨後加入教會旗下的經紀公司，繼續表演活動，話題一波接一波，2日又被爆出要和教主的兒子結婚了！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2564/d2564952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2564%2Fd2564952.jpg&h=38d8f3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清水富美加出家4個月，剪去招牌長髮，又傳出要嫁給教主的兒子大川宏洋。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2563/d2563213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2563%2Fd2563213.jpg&h=58d7307e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據日雜《NEWS POST SEVEN》報導，清水富美加出家4個月以來，從螢幕寵兒變成教徒，現在逐步復出，還和「幸福的科學」教主大川隆法一起出書，雖然被指責成了宗教的活招牌，仍然強調「這是我自己選擇的。」有教徒透露，她即將和教主的28歲兒子大川宏洋結婚，以後會逐漸成為宗教繼承者的妻子，成為教團的中心人物。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2564/d2564950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2564%2Fd2564950.jpg&h=7afdf4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清水富美加和「幸福的科學」教主大川隆法一起出書。<br />\n<br />\n清水富美加成為教團的簽約藝人，今後接拍教團出資的電影，勢必是主演級的人物，大川宏洋外型帥氣，兩人被力拱一起演出。有關婚訊傳言，她的經紀公司僅以簡短文字回應「這不是事實。」不過娛樂圈人士認為，她出家引發一連串騷動，加上雙親高中以來就離婚，對結婚建立家庭有很強的願望，被認為很有可能成為教主的媳婦。"},{"pid":"4806edb48eb48f1e8da1ebf1b4b7f80f34bceb0a","tid":268982,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:07:07.000Z","msg":"邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1e124dbc8cf3d77752e80bd87e41a2b74c1ed3","tid":268982,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"拍變態超人痴左"},{"pid":"924c0e26915a54b030b1c710e9cd6095f9b8c456","tid":268982,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"點解日本可以咁多呢啲邪教<br />\n生活壓力太大？"},{"pid":"7deb65df945f41404c83fc98f0f2ed4892209e18","tid":268982,"uid":38744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"日本啲邪教真係好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"59be7179356fbede486612eeb7bd08a64ecbb4d1","tid":268982,"uid":61529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本啲邪教真係好撚恐怖</blockquote><br />\n韓國啲邪教都係"},{"pid":"2dd82aa3e504d2372cd292b04a9496b0d92fd394","tid":268982,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f848c2da2f9e151289ce40fd5fa578385c295ac0","tid":268982,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:13:10.000Z","msg":"邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b151c12f0f70938ccbd21b5fdf0683d23f047d38","tid":268982,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢個本書出左未？</blockquote><br />\n出左 睇前半會覺得佢好慘 <br />\n後半想屌鬼"},{"pid":"1a5f36368fca666db7d98edb8049dd028ffa87e1","tid":268982,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"老爺會唔會幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}